data.description: Desirable 4 bedroom 2.5 bath move in ready custom built home with wrap around front porch and huge outdoor space featuring an inground pool on private 2 acre lot! This home features wood floors throughout the first floor, living room, dining room and breakfast room with gas fireplace that opens up to the kitchen which features an island with gas stove, pantry and wood cabinets. Huge laundry room with walkout to covered porch over looking pool! Partially finished basement boasts an exercise area or potential home office and huge family room with second fireplace! The spacious primary bedroom suite features his/her walk-in closets and luxurious adjoining bath! Minutes from kayaking, fishing, and sail boating at Cowan Lake! Also located in close proximity to the World Equestrian Center in Wilmington, Ohio! An absolute must see!
